# NestJS + Vercel (dnd-api)

1. Skill global `vercel` + local `nest-vercel-deploy`.
2. Entrypoint `src/main.ts` — `bootstrap()` + `app.listen(process.env.PORT ?? 3000)`.
3. TypeORM DataSource singleton; pooler 6543; app stateless.
4. JWT: `jsonwebtoken` + JWKS (sem `jose` no runtime).
